declarations.comments:
Execute a typed SQL query and parse results with yoga-json

Example:
  query = sql $ "SELECT * FROM users WHERE age > " ^ int @"minAge" ^ " AND name = " ^ str @"name"
  users <- executeSql @User query { minAge: 25, name: "Alice" } conn
